      • validateAppointmentInput

        public static boolean validateAppointmentInput​(int appointmentID,
                                               java.lang.String title,
                                               java.lang.String description,
                                               java.lang.String location,
                                               java.lang.String type,
                                               java.time.ZonedDateTime startTime,
                                               java.time.ZonedDateTime endTime,
                                               java.lang.String customerID,
                                               java.lang.String userID)
        Method to validate all fields from appointment input form, including checking whether appointment start and end are within business hours
        Parameters:
        appointmentID - int value of automatically generated appointment ID
        title - user-provided title string
        description - user-provided description string
        location - user-provided location
        type - user-provided type
        startTime - time and date of appointment start with user's timezone information
        endTime - time and date of appointment end with user's timezone information
        customerID - int value for ID of customer associated with appointment
        userID - int value for ID of user who created appointment
        Returns:
        bool indicating success of appointment input validation
